gmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96b443433482cdca3013c1db849ff51290a3fe5","tid":1595200,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b7db5c8f20d74434ee528c94a4138069dbaa27","tid":1595200,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8614c8afadcbb9f606cffb81b02ef382fb1a61be","tid":1595200,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b26c67ea781f39bd39b58aecaed9b3ebf074220c","tid":1595200,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUTErkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUTErkD.jpg&h=d1795672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[<a href=\"https://t.me/freedomofsummer]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreedomofsummer%5D&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=10ff17d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/freedomofsummer]</a><br />\n<br />\n前post <br />\n//你地開心啦，尋晚中秋前線小朋友食得一個包咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567456</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區//<br />\n<br />\n又係我地&quot;前線唔好餓死&quot;，為左更加易記，我地正式改名為&quot;前線肉成計劃。Freedom of Summer&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我地係幾個讀左幾年社會大學既90後，睇左《前線就黎餓死喇》呢個post而決定組織呢個計劃。經過左3個星期既努力，我地先餵到個幾百個手足... 每次上街都有幾萬人，多則幾十萬，未搵我地既手足求下你唔好猶豫，請立刻搵我地。<br />\n<br />\n正所謂&quot;士可殺，不可餓&quot;，食飽飯，自然跑得快。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，因為手足數量增加緊，仲增加得愈來愈快，我地需要大量飯卷，請有意既家長們未加入既快加入。已加入既留意channel，我地係長期計劃，有多餘錢既家長們可以每星期/每兩星期咁買飯卷幫手足。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n/////最普通運作Q&amp;A嘅係舊post有，我見普遍家長對呢樣野都冇咩大嘅疑問，下面我哋解答下家長最近比較多嘅問題。<br />\n<br />\nQ1: 買咩飯券/現金券比較好？<br />\nA1: 小朋友就比較鍾意超市券/大家樂/KFC/鴻福堂，希望如果家長想買可以買呢幾個。<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 點解全部都係大集團？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA2: 無可否認，大集團的而且確係最可以覆蓋到每個小朋友住嘅地方、學校附近......暫時對於我哋同佢哋黎講，呢個會係最方便同最有效嘅做法。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 有冇考慮同黃絲小店合作？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA3: 有，但係有兩點考量。<br />\n<br />\ni/ 我地人手有限，知道都有好多人希望可以幫手做義工，好多謝你地。但係為咗保障返我地，同埋避免不必要嘅爭拗，我地暫時唔會公開招募義工，希望可以理解。<br />\n<br />\nii/ 有個小店老闆好好人，主動聯絡左我哋可以提供食物，我哋亦都有同啲小朋友講過呢個情況，但普遍其實佢哋都唔係太願意露面。希望大家明白，對於佢哋黎講要匿名攞飯券已經係勇氣既一大步，呢個亦都係最真實嘅情況。<br />\n<br />\n因此，我哋暫時唔會有主動聯絡黃絲小店合作嘅計劃，如果大家有意見嘅話可以提出。<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n光復香港。時代革命<br />\n五大訴求。缺一不可<br />\n兄弟爬山。各自努力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"小店都賣餐券得唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T03:55:35.000Z","msg":"希望有小店自發推出, 我地暫時都唔夠人手去做小店合作<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b64d1494e5b1b82eb7f2197a176a7bb5de4686","tid":1595200,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5b7db5c8f20d74434ee528c94a4138069dbaa27","tid":1595200,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8614c8afadcbb9f606cffb81b02ef382fb1a61be","tid":1595200,"uid":70013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b26c67ea781f39bd39b58aecaed9b3ebf074220c","tid":1595200,"uid":164378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T02:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YUTErkD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYUTErkD.jpg&h=d1795672&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n[<a href=\"https://t.me/freedomofsummer]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffreedomofsummer%5D&d=9VpADaqRjl%2F0kIpcX62WRswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=10ff17d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/freedomofsummer]</a><br />\n<br />\n前post <br />\n//你地開心啦，尋晚中秋前線小朋友食得一個包咋<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://l